      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a great start. i like the phrasing 'indispensable instrument'. can you expand on that? like, specifically address why the common counter-argument about meritocracy is basically a flawed way of looking at the problem? i want to show that the idea that 'people just get what they deserve based on hard work' ignores the actual structural reality.",
